pect to an advance made or other value given by a secured party, means pursuant to the secured party\u8217\'3fs obligation, whether or not a subsequent event of default or other event not within the secured party\u8217\'3fs control has relieved or may relieve the secured party from its obligation.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{bx.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fRecord\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, except as used in }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3ffor record\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fof record\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3frecord or legal title\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, and }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3frecord owner\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, means information that is inscribed on a tangible medium or which is stored in an electronic or other medium and is retrievable in perceivable form.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{by.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fRegistered organization\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ means an organization formed or organized solely under the law of a single state or the United States by the filing of a public organic record with, the issuance of a public organic record by, or the enactment of legislation by the state or the United States. The term includes a business trust that is formed under the law of a single state if a statute of the state governing business trusts requires that the business trust\u8217\'3fs organic record be filed with the state.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{bz.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fSecondary obligor\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ m