\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{Unless a change in law has clearly been made, the provisions of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{ as amended shall be deemed declaratory of the meaning of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{ prior to amendment.}\par}{}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{[C75, 77, 79, }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{81, \'a7554.11108}}}{]}\par}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2000 Acts, ch 1149, \'a7155, 187}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\sb219\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{ }{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj}{{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{554.11109}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E17_2E11_2E2_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E17_2E11_2E2_2E2}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Effect of official comments.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{To the extent that they are consistent with the Iowa statutory text, the 1972 Official Comments to the 1972 Official Text of the Uniform Commercial Code are evidence of legislative intent as to the meaning of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this chapter}}}{ as amended by }\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cf5{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\cf5{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.legis.iowa.gov/docs/acts/1974/CH1249.pdf" }{\fldrslt \cf5 \f5 \fs18{{1974 Iowa Acts, ch.1249}}}}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{. However, prior drafts of the Official Text and Comments may not be used to ascertain legislative intent.}\par}{}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{[C75, 77, 79, }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{81, \'a7554.11109}}}{]}\par}{}{\pard\pla